Prerequisites:
    - NodeJS
    - MongoDB

Note: This webapp runs best in Chrome

Setting up the webapp:
    1) open a shell
    1) navigate to the project directory
    1) run "npm install"

Running the webapp:
    1) Make sure that MongoDB running (To start use shell cmd: mongod)
    2) Open a shell and run: nodejs app.js
    3) Go to https://localhost:3000 in the Chrome browser
